{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bb1feb7c40","title":"制城打援各个牙灭商丘硕山之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"48cff67d2a","index":0,"year":1947,"month":2,"day":7,"articleId":"bb1feb7c40"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9bc10545ef","type":"paragraph","text":"制城打援各个牙灭商丘硕山之敌”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bb1feb7c40"},{"id":"19de1e8cae","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年2月7日）刘，并转邓：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bb1feb7c40"},{"id":"021f9fb798","type":"paragraph","text":"我路南部队连克数城，又歼十六旅大部，自应休息数目，然后向北与主力靠拢，用围城打援方法吸引商杨巴之敌，各个歼灭之今后一时期内，你们全军任务是各个轩灭敌正规军，先打五军及七十五师，并准备打七十二师、八十五师及四十九旅。同时令路南、路北各地方兵团奇取薄弱城镇，收复失地","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bb1feb7c40"},{"id":"2b4bf68bfa","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bb1feb7c40"},{"id":"1ac81e6a2a","type":"paragraph","text":"丑虞西[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给晋翼兽豫野战军司令员刘伯承并转政治委员邓小平的电报。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bb1feb7c40"}],"page":{"id":"ceb8ab04c6","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bb1feb7c40","start":426,"end":426}}}},"__N_SSG":true}